{"tid":2446173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"漁護署聯同水警截獲非法拖網漁船 拘9內地漁民 明日提堂","createTime":"2021-03-14T08:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T10:01:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7e1929fe6d1a1aa14e287a67fe06b0513afa8561","tid":2446173,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"漁護署與水警本月12日（上周五）在石牛洲附近香港水域內一帶，進行打擊非法捕魚的聯合行動時，發現一艘懷疑正在拖網捕魚的蝦拖漁船，遂截停有關船隻進行調查，其後人員在船上撿走一批捕魚工具。船上9名內地漁民涉嫌違反《漁業保護規例》（《規例》）使用已被禁止的器具捕魚而被落案檢控，明日將於粉嶺裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署發言人提醒市民，禁止拖網捕魚措施已於2012年12月31起生效。根據《規例》，任何人士使用已被禁止的器具捕魚，一經定罪最高可被判罰款港幣二十萬元及監禁六個月。<br />\n<br />\n發言人強調，拖網捕魚是非選擇性的捕魚方法，會破壞海床及損害海洋生態。禁止拖網捕魚活動可即時遏止海洋資源損耗的情況，使海洋生態逐漸恢復至可持續發展的水平，長遠得到更有效的保護，將來會繼續與警方採取聯合執法行動，嚴厲打擊非法捕魚活動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210314/3UHH7KJ5ANFLZJNYK6UUVRIUGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210314%2F3UHH7KJ5ANFLZJNYK6UUVRIUGU%2F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=a408122f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210314%2F3UHH7KJ5ANFLZJNYK6UUVRIUGU%2F&h=031f35a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210314/3UHH7KJ5ANFLZJNYK6UUVRIUGU/</a>"},{"pid":"2e98c2f8660d12586bbf51805da8b7c2944e053b","tid":2446173,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"罰款500?"},{"pid":"db3b8649c14b517db49a266ba5526ad293c3408a","tid":2446173,"uid":8636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"支那狗撚會有事？"},{"pid":"e003ff38770246f0ef6a1c1ba586339fcb0d161e","tid":2446173,"uid":1069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:05:55.000Z","msg":"非法入境，599G 全部告埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64ebb14bea6fdd42ac1ed83810fc0be4ed9409a9","tid":2446173,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"拉去坐半年啦屌"},{"pid":"1037ee5196d1f88a21c08ac97cc8860ab6a06820","tid":2446173,"uid":227588,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2e98c2f8660d12586bbf51805da8b7c2944e053b","tid":2446173,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T08:52:33.000Z","msg":"罰款500?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:17:42.000Z","msg":"罰漁護署？"},{"pid":"e221abce2f5d06371bde69c361e43fd130ef8c09","tid":2446173,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:19:33.000Z","msg":"睇死d狗官唔會從非法捕魚推論出世界末日呢個結論"},{"pid":"13b89cbd8582945234883d4c6f0ba1f29606fed1","tid":2446173,"uid":262557,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:21:31.000Z","msg":"根本成個港水都係支那船係度捕魚捉野<br />\n有出海釣魚既巴打就會知"},{"pid":"26da14f8205d4f768a8b6e6e418e683fc61f2966","tid":2446173,"uid":16164,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:23:41.000Z","msg":"非法偷越邊境罪喎<br />\n唔學大陸困返幾條支那佬百幾日先上庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40ba12151db1789572bf4b71a5b1e16bed5436f","tid":2446173,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T09:43:00.000Z","msg":"即日就放人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc1989212858fbcf5b5c7e87c76c88987cb5dd6a","tid":2446173,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"鄭紀寒,莫梓沖會唔會推論非法拖網漁船涉及國際人口販運"}]}